      "status": "partial",
      "notes": "Supports callback-oriented completion/error observation for the current Readable, Writable, Duplex, Transform, and PassThrough implementations by monitoring end, finish, error, and premature close signals. Omitting the callback returns a Promise-backed observer from the same runtime path, but node:stream/promises is still out of scope.",
